thread.title: Many Asia Markets Rebound From Losses

author: Kenan Machado
title: Many Asia Markets Rebound From Losses
text:
S&P 500, Dow industrials remain on track for quarterly losses Tech stocks rise Energy stocks lead S&P 500 higher The Dow Jones Industrial Average rose more than 300 points Thursday as technology shares rebounded, but the blue-chip index remains on pace to suffer its first quarterly loss in more than two years.
